{
  "left": "<div>Foreword </div><div>by Paul Demiéville Member of the Institut de France,\nProfessor at the College de France\nDirector of Buddhist Studies at the School\nof Higher Studies (Paris) </div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div>Here is an exposition of Buddhism conceived in a resolutely modern spirit by one of the most qualified and enlightened representatives of that religion. The Rev. Dr. W. Rahula received the traditional training and education of a Buddhist monk in Ceylon, and held eminent positions in one of the leading monastic institutes (Pirivena) in that island, where the Law of the Buddha flourishes from the time of Asoka and has preserved all its vitality up to this day. Thus brought up in an ancient tradition, he decided, at this time when all traditions are called in question, to face the spirit and the methods of international scientific learning. He entered the Ceylon University, obtained the B.A. Honours degree (London), and then won the degree of Doctor of Philosophy of the Ceylon University on a highly learned thesis on the History of Buddhism in Ceylon. Having worked with distinguished professors at the University of Calcutta and come in contact with adepts of Mahāyāna (the Great Vehicle), that form of Buddhism which reigns from Tibet to the Far East, he decided to go into the Tibetan and Chinese texts in order to widen his œcumenism, and he has honoured us by coming to the University of Paris (Sorbonne) to prepare a study of Asanga, the illustrious philosopher of Mahāyāna, whose principal works in the original Sanskrit are lost, and can only be read in their Tibetan and Chinese translations. It is now eight years since Dr. Rahula is among us, wearing the yellow robe, breathing the air of the Occident, searching perhaps in our old troubled mirror a universalized reflection of the religion which is his. The book, which he has kindly asked me to present to the public of the West, is a luminous account, within reach of everybody, of the fundamental principles of the Buddhist doctrine, as they are found in the most ancient texts, which are called ‘The Tradition’ (Āgama) in Sanskrit and ‘The Canonic Corpus’ (Nikāyā) in Pali. Dr. Rahula, who possesses an incomparable knowledge of these texts, refers to them constantly and almost exclusively. Their authority is recognized unanimously by all the Buddhist schools, which were and are numerous, but none of which ever deviates from these texts, except with the intention of better interpreting the spirit beyond the letter. The interpretation has indeed been varied in the course of the expansion of Buddhism through many centuries and vast regions, and the Law has taken more than one aspect. But the aspect of Buddhism here presented by Dr. Rahula—humanist, rational, Socratic in some respects, Evangelic in others, or again almost scientific—has for its support a great deal of authentic scriptural evidence which he only had to let speak for themselves. The explanations which he adds to his quotations, always translated with scrupulous accuracy, are clear, simple, direct, and free from all pedantry. Some among them might lead to discussion, as when he wishes to rediscover in the Pali sources all the doctrines of Mahāyāna; but his familiarity with those sources permits him to throw new light on them. He addresses himself to the modern man, but he refrains from insisting on comparisons just suggested here and there, which could be made with certain currents of thought of the contemporary world: socialism, atheism, existentialism, psycho-analysis. It is for the reader to appreciate the modernity, the possibilities of adaptation of a doctrine which, in this work of genuine scholarship, is presented to him in its primal richness.\n\nRahula, Walpola. What the Buddha Taught (English Edition) (pp. 11-13). (Function). Kindle Edition. </div>",
  "right": "<h1 data-section-id=\"1jvo4v3\" data-start=\"123\" data-end=\"137\" class=\"PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">Foreword（序文）<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"PDq2pG_selectionAnchor\"></span></h1><p data-start=\"138\" data-end=\"160\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><strong data-start=\"138\" data-end=\"160\">by Paul Demiéville</strong></p><p data-start=\"162\" data-end=\"316\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">Paul Demiéville<br>Member of the Institut de France,<br>Professor at the College de France,<br>Director of Buddhist Studies at the School of Higher Studies (Paris)</p><p data-start=\"318\" data-end=\"327\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">まず著者紹介です。</p><ul data-start=\"329\" data-end=\"407\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><li data-section-id=\"irj0gd\" data-start=\"329\" data-end=\"344\">Foreword = 序文</li><li data-section-id=\"1qtt3g8\" data-start=\"345\" data-end=\"356\">by = ～による</li><li data-section-id=\"yv9a72\" data-start=\"357\" data-end=\"370\">Member = 会員</li><li data-section-id=\"4hgsdz\" data-start=\"371\" data-end=\"387\">Professor = 教授</li><li data-section-id=\"1kgyabi\" data-start=\"388\" data-end=\"407\">Director = 学科長・主任</li></ul><p data-start=\"409\" data-end=\"412\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">つまり</p><blockquote data-start=\"414\" data-end=\"446\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"416\" data-end=\"446\">「フランスを代表する東洋学者ポール・デミエヴィルによる序文」</p></blockquote><p data-start=\"448\" data-end=\"459\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">という意味になります。</p><hr data-start=\"461\" data-end=\"464\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h1 data-section-id=\"1psefh\" data-start=\"466\" data-end=\"471\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">第一文</h1><blockquote data-start=\"473\" data-end=\"627\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"475\" data-end=\"627\">Here is an exposition of Buddhism conceived in a resolutely modern spirit by one of the most qualified and enlightened representatives of that religion.</p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"629\" data-end=\"632\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1y2aktx\" data-start=\"634\" data-end=\"648\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">スラッシュリーディング</h2><p data-start=\"650\" data-end=\"812\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">Here is<br>/ an exposition of Buddhism<br>/ conceived<br>/ in a resolutely modern spirit<br>/ by one of the most qualified and enlightened representatives<br>/ of that religion.</p><hr data-start=\"814\" data-end=\"817\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"14wt4xg\" data-start=\"819\" data-end=\"827\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">語順どおり</h2><p data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"840\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><strong data-start=\"829\" data-end=\"840\">Here is</strong></p><p data-start=\"842\" data-end=\"851\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ ここにあるのは</p><hr data-start=\"853\" data-end=\"856\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"887\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><strong data-start=\"858\" data-end=\"887\">an exposition of Buddhism</strong></p><p data-start=\"889\" data-end=\"903\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ 仏教についての解説である</p><hr data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"908\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"910\" data-end=\"923\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><strong data-start=\"910\" data-end=\"923\">conceived</strong></p><p data-start=\"925\" data-end=\"932\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ 構想された</p><hr data-start=\"934\" data-end=\"937\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"939\" data-end=\"972\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><strong data-start=\"939\" data-end=\"972\">in a resolutely modern spirit</strong></p><p data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"987\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ 徹底して現代的な精神で</p><hr data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"992\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"994\" data-end=\"1058\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><strong data-start=\"994\" data-end=\"1058\">by one of the most qualified and enlightened representatives</strong></p><p data-start=\"1060\" data-end=\"1096\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ その宗教を代表する<br>最も資格があり<br>最も見識の深い人物の一人によって</p><hr data-start=\"1098\" data-end=\"1101\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"1103\" data-end=\"1123\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><strong data-start=\"1103\" data-end=\"1123\">of that religion</strong></p><p data-start=\"1125\" data-end=\"1137\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ その宗教（仏教）の。</p><hr data-start=\"1139\" data-end=\"1142\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1dzuv8g\" data-start=\"1144\" data-end=\"1151\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">自然な訳</h2><blockquote data-start=\"1153\" data-end=\"1214\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"1155\" data-end=\"1214\">「ここにあるのは、仏教を代表する最も見識ある人物の一人が、徹底して現代的な精神に基づいてまとめた仏教の解説書である。」</p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"1216\" data-end=\"1219\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1mwskj\" data-start=\"1221\" data-end=\"1226\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">単語</h2><h3 data-section-id=\"11sgbaa\" data-start=\"1228\" data-end=\"1242\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">exposition</h3><p data-start=\"1244\" data-end=\"1256\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">説明<br>解説<br>体系的な紹介</p><p data-start=\"1258\" data-end=\"1283\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">普通の explanation より堅い表現です。</p><hr data-start=\"1285\" data-end=\"1288\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"vmvkvw\" data-start=\"1290\" data-end=\"1303\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">conceived</h3><p data-start=\"1305\" data-end=\"1313\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">conceive</p><p data-start=\"1315\" data-end=\"1328\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">「考え出す」<br>「構想する」</p><p data-start=\"1330\" data-end=\"1334\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">ここでは</p><blockquote data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1353\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"1338\" data-end=\"1353\">conceived in...</p></blockquote><p data-start=\"1355\" data-end=\"1370\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">「～という考え方で構想された」</p><hr data-start=\"1372\" data-end=\"1375\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"xlunw0\" data-start=\"1377\" data-end=\"1391\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">resolutely</h3><p data-start=\"1393\" data-end=\"1403\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">断固として<br>徹底して</p><hr data-start=\"1405\" data-end=\"1408\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"1d8p2hv\" data-start=\"1410\" data-end=\"1420\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">spirit</h3><p data-start=\"1422\" data-end=\"1426\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">ここでは</p><p data-start=\"1428\" data-end=\"1430\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">精神</p><p data-start=\"1432\" data-end=\"1434\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">思想</p><p data-start=\"1436\" data-end=\"1438\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">理念</p><hr data-start=\"1440\" data-end=\"1443\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"14o0y20\" data-start=\"1445\" data-end=\"1458\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">qualified</h3><p data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1465\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">資格のある</p><p data-start=\"1467\" data-end=\"1472\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">能力の高い</p><hr data-start=\"1474\" data-end=\"1477\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"5nb7q1\" data-start=\"1479\" data-end=\"1494\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">enlightened</h3><p data-start=\"1496\" data-end=\"1499\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">悟った</p><p data-start=\"1501\" data-end=\"1506\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">啓発された</p><p data-start=\"1508\" data-end=\"1515\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">深い知識を持つ</p><p data-start=\"1517\" data-end=\"1533\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">仏教では非常に意味深い単語です。</p><hr data-start=\"1535\" data-end=\"1538\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"g3db1p\" data-start=\"1540\" data-end=\"1553\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">この文で伝えたいこと</h2><p data-start=\"1555\" data-end=\"1570\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">ポール・デミエヴィルはいきなり</p><p data-start=\"1572\" data-end=\"1590\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">「これは普通の仏教本ではありません」</p><p data-start=\"1592\" data-end=\"1600\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">と言っています。</p><p data-start=\"1602\" data-end=\"1605\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">つまり</p><blockquote data-start=\"1607\" data-end=\"1635\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1635\"><strong data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1635\">伝統仏教を現代人にも理解できるように書いた本</strong></p></blockquote><p data-start=\"1637\" data-end=\"1647\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">だと宣言しています。</p><hr data-start=\"1649\" data-end=\"1652\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h1 data-section-id=\"1ptji9\" data-start=\"1654\" data-end=\"1659\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">第二文</h1><blockquote data-start=\"1661\" data-end=\"1763\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"1663\" data-end=\"1763\">The Rev. Dr. W. Rahula received the traditional training and education of a Buddhist monk in Ceylon,</p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"1765\" data-end=\"1768\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"18oo4zo\" data-start=\"1770\" data-end=\"1778\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">スラッシュ</h2><p data-start=\"1780\" data-end=\"1802\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">The Rev. Dr. W. Rahula</p><p data-start=\"1804\" data-end=\"1814\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">/ received</p><p data-start=\"1816\" data-end=\"1856\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">/ the traditional training and education</p><p data-start=\"1858\" data-end=\"1878\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">/ of a Buddhist monk</p><p data-start=\"1880\" data-end=\"1892\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">/ in Ceylon.</p><hr data-start=\"1894\" data-end=\"1897\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1m16f1\" data-start=\"1899\" data-end=\"1904\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">語順</h2><p data-start=\"1906\" data-end=\"1928\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">The Rev. Dr. W. Rahula</p><p data-start=\"1930\" data-end=\"1939\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ ラーフラ博士は</p><p data-start=\"1941\" data-end=\"1949\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">received</p><p data-start=\"1951\" data-end=\"1956\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ 受けた</p><p data-start=\"1958\" data-end=\"1996\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">the traditional training and education</p><p data-start=\"1998\" data-end=\"2010\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ 伝統的な修行と教育を</p><p data-start=\"2012\" data-end=\"2030\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">of a Buddhist monk</p><p data-start=\"2032\" data-end=\"2040\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ 仏教僧として</p><p data-start=\"2042\" data-end=\"2051\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">in Ceylon</p><p data-start=\"2053\" data-end=\"2070\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ セイロン（現在のスリランカ）で</p><hr data-start=\"2072\" data-end=\"2075\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1dzuv8g\" data-start=\"2077\" data-end=\"2084\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">自然な訳</h2><blockquote data-start=\"2086\" data-end=\"2134\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"2088\" data-end=\"2134\">「ラーフラ博士は、セイロン（現在のスリランカ）で、仏教僧として伝統的な修行と教育を受けた。」</p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2136\" data-end=\"2139\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1mwskj\" data-start=\"2141\" data-end=\"2146\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">単語</h2><h3 data-section-id=\"ynp8h5\" data-start=\"2148\" data-end=\"2156\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">Rev.</h3><p data-start=\"2158\" data-end=\"2166\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">Reverend</p><p data-start=\"2168\" data-end=\"2170\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">牧師</p><p data-start=\"2172\" data-end=\"2174\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">僧侶</p><p data-start=\"2176\" data-end=\"2183\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">宗教者への敬称</p><hr data-start=\"2185\" data-end=\"2188\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"z19q71\" data-start=\"2190\" data-end=\"2214\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">traditional training</h3><p data-start=\"2216\" data-end=\"2221\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">伝統的修行</p><hr data-start=\"2223\" data-end=\"2226\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"nt1my4\" data-start=\"2228\" data-end=\"2241\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">education</h3><p data-start=\"2243\" data-end=\"2245\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">教育</p><p data-start=\"2247\" data-end=\"2249\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">学問</p><hr data-start=\"2251\" data-end=\"2254\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"emziok\" data-start=\"2256\" data-end=\"2266\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">Ceylon</h3><p data-start=\"2268\" data-end=\"2271\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">現在の</p><p data-start=\"2273\" data-end=\"2314\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><strong data-start=\"2273\" data-end=\"2314\">Sri Lanka</strong></p><hr data-start=\"2316\" data-end=\"2319\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h1 data-section-id=\"yhq5bl\" data-start=\"2321\" data-end=\"2325\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">続き</h1><blockquote data-start=\"2327\" data-end=\"2424\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"2329\" data-end=\"2424\">and held eminent positions in one of the leading monastic institutes (Pirivena) in that island,</p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2426\" data-end=\"2429\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"18oo4zo\" data-start=\"2431\" data-end=\"2439\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">スラッシュ</h2><p data-start=\"2441\" data-end=\"2449\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">and held</p><p data-start=\"2451\" data-end=\"2470\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">/ eminent positions</p><p data-start=\"2472\" data-end=\"2515\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">/ in one of the leading monastic institutes</p><p data-start=\"2517\" data-end=\"2529\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">/ (Pirivena)</p><p data-start=\"2531\" data-end=\"2547\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">/ in that island</p><hr data-start=\"2549\" data-end=\"2552\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1m16f1\" data-start=\"2554\" data-end=\"2559\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">語順</h2><p data-start=\"2561\" data-end=\"2569\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">and held</p><p data-start=\"2571\" data-end=\"2579\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ そして務めた</p><p data-start=\"2581\" data-end=\"2598\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">eminent positions</p><p data-start=\"2600\" data-end=\"2605\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ 要職を</p><p data-start=\"2607\" data-end=\"2648\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">in one of the leading monastic institutes</p><p data-start=\"2650\" data-end=\"2662\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ 有数の僧院教育機関で</p><p data-start=\"2664\" data-end=\"2674\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">(Pirivena)</p><p data-start=\"2676\" data-end=\"2686\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">→ ピリヴェナという</p><hr data-start=\"2688\" data-end=\"2691\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1dzuv8g\" data-start=\"2693\" data-end=\"2700\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">自然な訳</h2><blockquote data-start=\"2702\" data-end=\"2742\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><p data-start=\"2704\" data-end=\"2742\">「さらに、島内でも有数の僧院教育機関（ピリヴェナ）で重要な役職を歴任した。」</p></blockquote><hr data-start=\"2744\" data-end=\"2747\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h2 data-section-id=\"1mwskj\" data-start=\"2749\" data-end=\"2754\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">単語</h2><h3 data-section-id=\"ylsgwm\" data-start=\"2756\" data-end=\"2767\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">eminent</h3><p data-start=\"2769\" data-end=\"2772\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">著名な</p><p data-start=\"2774\" data-end=\"2777\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">重要な</p><p data-start=\"2779\" data-end=\"2782\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">優れた</p><hr data-start=\"2784\" data-end=\"2787\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"rbypwm\" data-start=\"2789\" data-end=\"2801\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">monastic</h3><p data-start=\"2803\" data-end=\"2807\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">修道院の</p><p data-start=\"2809\" data-end=\"2812\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">僧院の</p><hr data-start=\"2814\" data-end=\"2817\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"hz91kv\" data-start=\"2819\" data-end=\"2832\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">institute</h3><p data-start=\"2834\" data-end=\"2838\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">教育機関</p><p data-start=\"2840\" data-end=\"2844\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">研究機関</p><hr data-start=\"2846\" data-end=\"2849\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h1 data-section-id=\"464005\" data-start=\"2851\" data-end=\"2860\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">今日のポイント</h1><p data-start=\"2862\" data-end=\"2979\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">この序文の冒頭だけで、著者紹介にかなりのページを使っています。これは、「ラーフラ博士は単なる学者ではなく、<strong data-start=\"2915\" data-end=\"2955\">伝統的な仏教の修行・教育を受けた僧侶でありながら、西洋の学問も修めた人物</strong>である」という本書の信頼性を読者に示すためです。</p><p data-start=\"2981\" data-end=\"3079\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">あなたが以前から研究している「<strong data-start=\"2996\" data-end=\"3026\">仏教を現代科学やFEP、生命論と結び付けて理解したい</strong>」というテーマとも重なります。ラーフラ自身がまさに「伝統」と「現代科学」の橋渡しを目指した人物だからです。</p><hr data-start=\"3081\" data-end=\"3084\" style=\"white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><h3 data-section-id=\"zk11x0\" data-start=\"3086\" data-end=\"3097\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">学習アドバイス</h3><p data-start=\"3099\" data-end=\"3132\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">この本は、単に英語を訳すだけではもったいない内容です。今後は毎回、</p><ol data-start=\"3134\" data-end=\"3250\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><li data-section-id=\"u35q7e\" data-start=\"3134\" data-end=\"3148\">スラッシュリーディング</li><li data-section-id=\"i92xqb\" data-start=\"3149\" data-end=\"3160\">語順どおりの理解</li><li data-section-id=\"1u9ahgq\" data-start=\"3161\" data-end=\"3171\">自然な日本語訳</li><li data-section-id=\"24x55o\" data-start=\"3172\" data-end=\"3182\">重要単語・文法</li><li data-section-id=\"1wyqrlj\" data-start=\"3183\" data-end=\"3212\">「仏教では何を伝えようとしているのか」という内容解説</li><li data-section-id=\"p43v0v\" data-start=\"3213\" data-end=\"3250\">必要に応じて、あなたの「時間＝生命」「縁」の考え方や現代科学との接点</li></ol><p data-start=\"3252\" data-end=\"3287\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\">という流れで読み進めれば、英語と仏教の両方を深く理解できると思います。</p>",
  "sync": false
}
